
Creacion de tabla Users:

 - CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users ( users_id INTEGER GENERATED ALWAYS AS IDENTIFY PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL, email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL, password VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL);

Creacion de tabla:

Creacion de tabla Groups:

 - CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS groups (groups_id INTEGER GENERATED ALWAYS AS PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL, purpose TEXT, debt DECIMAL(10, 2) DEFAULT 0.00 );


 - CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS groups (
    groups_id INTEGER GENERATED ALWAYS AS PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    purpose TEXT,
    debt DECIMAL(10, 2) DEFAULT 0.00
);

Creacion de tabla Expenses:

 - CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS expenses (expenses_id INTEGER GENERATED ALWAYS AS PRIMARY KEY, created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL, amount DOUBLE PRESICION NOT NULL description TEXT, created_by VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL, currency columna TIPODATO CHECK (Money));
 
